0.1.1.name: wordpress/haiku-minimalist-audio-player
0.1.1.description: A simple HTML5-based audio player that inserts a text link or graphical player for audio playback. Compatible with WP Audio Player style links, fully accessible and degrades gracefully, and includes Google Analytics tracking of audio plays. Based on jPlayer.
